# Google Drive integration (optional). When unset, Drive features stay hidden
# and the app saves to local offline versions only.
#
# Get a Client ID from Google Cloud Console:
#   1. Enable the Google Drive API
#   2. OAuth consent screen → add scope .../auth/drive.file
#   3. Create OAuth 2.0 "Web application" credentials
#   4. Add your origins (e.g. http://localhost:8080, https://<user>.github.io)
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the value.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
